                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen fuel cell system",
                    "一种氢燃料电池系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of fuel cells, and discloses a hydrogen fuel cell system. The electrochemical purification hydrogen circulation device is used for replacing a hydrogen circulation pump, hydrogen containing trace impurities flows into the fuel cell stack for reaction, excessive hydrogen containing impurities flows out of the fuel cell and then enters the electrochemical purification device, impurity gas is directly discharged, periodic impurity gas discharge is not needed, and the energy consumption is reduced. And the utilization rate of the hydrogen is improved while the working pressure of the stack gas is ensured to be stable. The hydrogen circulation volume of the system can be adjusted according to requirements, and the circulation volume and the fresh hydrogen inlet flow at an electric pile inlet are properly controlled, so that the uniformity of a flow field in the electric pile can be ensured, and the electric pile performance is improved. The purification device is composed of a metal bipolar plate, a diffusion layer, a catalyst layer and a proton exchange membrane, the metal bipolar plate is located in a hydrogen environment, purification can be achieved by applying extremely small voltage, and therefore the performance and the service life of the device can be guaranteed by using a low-cost coating."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及燃料电池技术领域，公开一种氢燃料电池系统。本发明利用电化学纯化氢循环装置替代氢气循环泵，含微量杂质的氢气流入燃料电池电堆内部反应，过量含杂质的氢气流出燃料电池后进入电化学纯化装置，杂质气体被直接排出，无需周期性的进行杂质气体排放，在保证电堆气体工作压力稳定的同时提高了氢气的利用率。系统的氢气循环量可以根据需求调节，适当控制循环量与电堆入口新鲜氢气进气流量，可保证电堆内部流场均匀性，提高电堆性能。纯化装置由金属双极板、扩散层、催化层和质子交换膜组成，其中，金属双极板处于氢气环境且外加极小的电压即可实现纯化，因此使用低成本涂层即可保证装置性能及寿命。"
                }
            ]
        }
